Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.48,0:00:04.45,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm back!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.30,0:00:10.48,main,,0000,0000,0000,,No one's home?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.01,0:00:22.32,main,,0000,0000,0000,,You've done well to make it this far.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.32,0:00:24.23,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Allow me to congratulate you.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.23,0:00:26.43,main,,0000,0000,0000,,This is my home...
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,main,,0000,0000,0000,,< OP >
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.24,0:02:04.21,main,,0000,0000,0000,,A screening? Of Meruru?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.05,0:02:06.00,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.00,0:02:07.48,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Why do you guys have to do it here?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.62,0:02:11.16,main,,0000,0000,0000,,A few days ago, in Akihabara...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.22,0:02:15.61,main,,0000,0000,0000,,What, you've only watched six episodes?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.90,0:02:19.69,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Quiet. I'm busy with my own life, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.69,0:02:22.91,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Be grateful that I've even watched to episode 6.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.69,0:02:26.75,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Frankly, it's incredibly boring.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.12,0:02:35.00,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Even with these eyes which far surpass humans', I can't find anything good in it.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.67,0:02:38.26,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe your eyes have gone bad from watching your Maschera.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.89,0:02:40.51,main,,0000,0000,0000,,What did you just say?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.51,0:02:42.71,main,,0000,0000,0000,,There, there, there!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.79,0:02:49.64,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Why don't we have a screening of Meruru and Maschera this Thursday then?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.51,0:02:51.20,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.94,0:02:55.76,main,,0000,0000,0000,,You two are always having the same argument.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.76,0:03:01.41,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Your prejudices might be preventing you from seeing each other's anime in a different light.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.41,0:03:03.41,main,,0000,0000,0000,,That's not—
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.94,0:03:10.08,main,,0000,0000,0000,,If we watch it together and offer commentary, you might find a new perspective.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.79,0:03:22.43,main,,0000,0000,0000,,So, Miss "My parents are always gone Thursdays so I can watch anime on the big screen in the living room! Yahoo!"
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.86,0:03:26.53,main,,0000,0000,0000,,...aka your little sister, gave in and agreed.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.53,0:03:28.23,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I see...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.05,0:03:30.43,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, then where's Kirino?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.59,0:03:34.19,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Her room, probably.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.87,0:03:36.33,main,,0000,0000,0000,,And Saori?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.33,0:03:38.44,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Something urgent came up so she can't make it.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.88,0:03:42.81,main,,0000,0000,0000,,So basically, it's just you and Kirino today?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.81,0:03:43.82,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.82,0:03:47.10,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I get it.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.10,0:03:48.68,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I get it now.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.48,0:03:51.12,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I get it perfectly.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.58,0:03:54.11,main,,0000,0000,0000,,You got into a fight with her.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.18,0:03:56.59,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Basically.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.09,0:04:07.47,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Mr. Kyousuke, the rest ‘tis left to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.01,0:04:11.35,main,,0000,0000,0000,,‘Tis really left to me, Miss Saori?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.83,0:04:16.48,main,,0000,0000,0000,,It's more trouble than I want, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.86,0:04:19.98,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I do owe Saori a lot.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.51,0:04:22.36,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Guess I'll have to.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.92,0:04:27.69,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Alright. Eat up.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.69,0:04:28.74,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Alright.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.67,0:04:31.84,main,,0000,0000,0000,,So, what did you get into a fight over?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.84,0:04:32.54,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Anime again?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.54,0:04:37.04,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Novels.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.45,0:04:39.80,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Novels?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.04,0:04:44.93,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Calling that aberration a novel goes against my principles, but your sister said,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.60,0:04:49.43,main,,0000,0000,0000,,"Oh, right. You wrote novels on some site or something, right?"
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.68,0:04:50.87,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Woah, that was scarily good!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.87,0:04:52.18,main,,0000,0000,0000,,She put her soul into that!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.54,0:04:56.31,main,,0000,0000,0000,,"I tried writing one too. Care to read it?"
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.31,0:04:59.44,main,,0000,0000,0000,,"Well, it's perfect, like everything else I do."
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.44,0:05:02.05,main,,0000,0000,0000,,That'd be enough to get me pissed off.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.05,0:05:02.88,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Right?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.88,0:05:04.95,main,,0000,0000,0000,,So, was it boring?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.46,0:05:10.20,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I wanted to kill her.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.37,0:05:12.20,main,,0000,0000,0000,,It was that bad??
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.64,0:05:15.85,main,,0000,0000,0000,,What was it about? I'm actually kind of curious now.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.85,0:05:17.21,main,,0000,0000,0000,,To start with,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.21,0:05:19.39,main,,0000,0000,0000,,the main character was a mirror image of the author.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.39,0:05:20.96,main,,0000,0000,0000,,She refers to herself with "atashi".
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.62,0:05:22.96,main,,0000,0000,0000,,That's not all.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.51,0:05:26.86,main,,0000,0000,0000,,She'll start a new paragraph after two or three words...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.86,0:05:28.84,main,,0000,0000,0000,,She'll start a new page just because she feels like it...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.84,0:05:31.72,main,,0000,0000,0000,,There are more symbols and emotes than actual words...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.72,0:05:34.75,main,,0000,0000,0000,,More than half of it is self-glorification.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.71,0:05:43.11,main,,0000,0000,0000,,And in the end, a goth loli character clearly modeled after me gets raped and dies.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.11,0:05:44.61,main,,0000,0000,0000,,That's so wrong!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.29,0:05:49.51,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Wow, yeah, that's definitely something to get angry about.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.06,0:05:51.69,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Go on. Eat up, eat up.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.69,0:05:54.12,main,,0000,0000,0000,,It won't make up for it, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.89,0:05:56.12,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.60,0:06:00.72,main,,0000,0000,0000,,But you write novels too?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.72,0:06:03.63,main,,0000,0000,0000,,No wonder you can point out flaws so easily.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.18,0:06:09.13,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I wouldn't be able to explain what's wrong with her novel.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.13,0:06:14.95,main,,0000,0000,0000,,It's hard to judge things like that unless you know how to write one properly yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.95,0:06:17.84,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I think you're misunderstanding things.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.08,0:06:22.72,main,,0000,0000,0000,,There is no "correct" for a work of literature.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.72,0:06:25.77,main,,0000,0000,0000,,However it's written, it can't be "wrong".
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.77,0:06:27.53,main,,0000,0000,0000,,That's what I think.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.53,0:06:33.03,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone has a different reason for writing, so that's just naturally how it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.45,0:06:36.79,main,,0000,0000,0000,,There can be no absolute correct way to write.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.42,0:06:43.29,main,,0000,0000,0000,,My complaints just now simply mean that it was not something I could enjoy.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.68,0:06:46.27,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't get me wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.72,0:06:49.93,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I see...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.37,0:06:51.68,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't get it at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.51,0:07:00.55,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, let me just go put this in my room.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.35,0:07:04.82,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Kirino!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.02,0:07:08.94,main,,0000,0000,0000,,You're there, right? Open up—
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.89,0:07:15.24,main,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.74,0:07:16.74,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Eroge.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.72,0:07:21.87,main,,0000,0000,0000,,What kind of host invites a friend over then goes to play eroge alone?{It would be fun to play eroge together.}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.87,0:07:23.38,main,,0000,0000,0000,,It's got nothing to do with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.89,0:07:26.63,main,,0000,0000,0000,,And anyway, she started it.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.58,0:07:28.74,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, right!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.74,0:07:34.11,main,,0000,0000,0000,,She said your novel has a character modeled after her that gets raped and dies!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.58,0:07:35.70,main,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.70,0:07:37.64,main,,0000,0000,0000,,What's she talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.61,0:07:40.31,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Here.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.76,0:07:41.75,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Read this.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.90,0:07:47.40,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Manga and a novel?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.71,0:07:49.76,main,,0000,0000,0000,,That Kuroneko...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.76,0:07:53.66,main,,0000,0000,0000,,That {\i1}Kuso{\i0}neko wrote this Maschera alternate ending doujinshi.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.08,0:07:55.75,main,,0000,0000,0000,,You didn't have to start over just to insult her...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.27,0:07:58.41,main,,0000,0000,0000,,So, what about this book?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.90,0:08:06.42,main,,0000,0000,0000,,"Hmph. Then while I read this novel that already smells like crap, you can read this."
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.42,0:08:07.80,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Woah, that was scarily good!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.80,0:08:08.92,main,,0000,0000,0000,,She put her soul into that!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.04,0:08:11.92,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Was it boring?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.23,0:08:14.05,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I wanted to kill her.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.05,0:08:15.97,main,,0000,0000,0000,,It was that bad??
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.48,0:08:17.97,main,,0000,0000,0000,,What's it about?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.10,0:08:28.23,main,,0000,0000,0000,,After the last boss of the first season, Queen of Nightmare, is defeated by Shikkoku, she gets shifted back in time to the start of the story.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.23,0:08:31.48,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, Shikkoku is Maschera's main character.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.48,0:08:38.49,main,,0000,0000,0000,,So she takes over the corpse of a girl that dies in the original story and gets closer to Shikkoku as a normal girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.49,0:08:41.58,main,,0000,0000,0000,,What's so bad about that though?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.58,0:08:42.92,main,,0000,0000,0000,,It actually sounds pretty interesting.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.92,0:08:43.85,main,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.85,0:08:46.94,main,,0000,0000,0000,,You flipped through the pages a little, and now you think you can comment on it?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.94,0:08:51.00,main,,0000,0000,0000,,The worst part of this book isn't that obvious.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.25,0:08:53.92,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Look at this! The page is practically black!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.92,0:08:55.73,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Over 90% of it is words.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.73,0:08:57.56,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Ever thought of starting a new paragraph?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.56,0:09:01.18,main,,0000,0000,0000,,And there are so many obscure words and idioms too!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.18,0:09:05.56,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Can't you just simply say "Boom!" when something explodes, or "Augh!" when someone gets hit?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.06,0:09:15.32,main,,0000,0000,0000,,On top of that, this doujinshi requires that you read this 200-page encyclopedia of errata, otherwise you won't understand half of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.57,0:09:19.52,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Basically, she just wrote this for her own self-gratification!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.52,0:09:22.33,main,,0000,0000,0000,,And what pisses me off most of all...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.58,0:09:28.46,main,,0000,0000,0000,,A loli character clearly modeled after me is the main character's sex slave!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.16,0:09:30.96,main,,0000,0000,0000,,That's definitely something to get angry about!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.96,0:09:32.64,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Right? Right?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.64,0:09:34.25,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn goth loli...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.25,0:09:36.97,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Turning my sister into a sex slave?!{Of course.}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.85,0:09:38.60,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.60,0:09:41.35,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Didn't I just do something just like this?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.56,0:09:43.88,main,,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.47,0:09:45.38,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.38,0:09:46.48,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait a second...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.48,0:09:49.73,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Did you actually read through that entire encyclopedia?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.89,0:09:52.73,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I wouldn't be able to complain if I didn't.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.70,0:09:56.36,main,,0000,0000,0000,,You guys really are good friends...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.14,0:09:59.31,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Alright. I get it.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.31,0:10:01.01,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I get it now.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.09,0:10:03.87,main,,0000,0000,0000,,How about this?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.34,0:10:07.03,main,,0000,0000,0000,,The point of this visit was a Meruru screening, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.55,0:10:09.37,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's try doing that then.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.74,0:10:13.12,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Otherwise, it'll just be a waste of your time.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.12,0:10:14.00,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Fine, I guess.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.37,0:10:18.23,main,,0000,0000,0000,,And isn't this your once-in-a-week chance to watch anime on the big screen?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.23,0:10:20.01,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Not like I care.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.42,0:10:23.01,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Saori?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.86,0:10:24.69,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Hello?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.69,0:10:26.90,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Mr. Kyousuke, it's me.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.90,0:10:28.48,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah. What's up?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.48,0:10:30.04,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm done over here.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.04,0:10:32.77,main,,0000,0000,0000,,How are things going on your front?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.84,0:10:38.84,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Right now, it seems the first cannon may be lit at any time.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.17,0:10:43.63,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry to keep you waiting!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.63,0:10:45.79,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Now then, let us begin our screening!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.15,0:10:48.14,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, you can't watch it like that!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.14,0:10:49.69,main,,0000,0000,0000,,You need not worry!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.69,0:10:53.11,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I will play it here at the same time.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.11,0:10:55.78,main,,0000,0000,0000,,We may be far separated, but we are of one mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.78,0:10:57.30,main,,0000,0000,0000,,A new definition for "live screening"...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.00,0:11:02.30,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Well then, let's start the screening.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.26,0:11:06.63,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Stardust Witch Meruru!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.56,0:11:10.27,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Starts now!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.00,0:11:10.27,overlap,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.61,0:11:12.27,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Meru-chan! Meru-chan! Meru-chan! Meru-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.62,0:11:14.77,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Why are you going crazy right from the start??
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.77,0:11:17.53,main,,0000,0000,0000,,My, it sounds like it's going well.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.10,0:11:21.28,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Stardust Witch Meruru, on the job!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.71,0:11:25.16,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, isn't this kinda sketchy?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.16,0:11:27.51,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Can they really show this on TV?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.51,0:11:29.59,main,,0000,0000,0000,,This is the DVD version.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.59,0:11:33.83,main,,0000,0000,0000,,For the TV broadcast, ribbons hide the little girl's naked body.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.83,0:11:35.13,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't call her a little girl!{http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=hwLLQlOKgJI}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.53,0:11:39.63,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Fans went wild when some station aired the uncensored version one time.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.13,0:11:42.04,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah... This is...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.04,0:11:43.26,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Kinda dangerous?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.06,0:11:51.81,main,,0000,0000,0000,,The first reason why I can't like this anime.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.08,0:11:53.69,main,,0000,0000,0000,,The opening theme is an electronic song.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.78,0:12:05.34,main,,0000,0000,0000,,With more force than (KIRA☆)
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.34,0:12:07.78,main,,0000,0000,0000,,A meteorite (KIRA☆)!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.75,0:12:27.80,main,,0000,0000,0000,,She's basically saying, "I'm going to release my full-power magic into you at point blank, so don't move, bitch".
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.41,0:12:36.94,main,,0000,0000,0000,,This girl can bombard her opponent with attacks with a smile on her face.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.94,0:12:37.96,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Disturbing.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.40,0:12:45.61,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Too many things these days mix loli and ero, and not just in anime either.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.61,0:12:50.33,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I can only weep over the fact that people keep buying this kind of vulgar crap.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.83,0:12:53.83,main,,0000,0000,0000,,The public needs to put more attention into maintaining an aesthetic sense.{I agree. Kuroneko = ore no yome~}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.83,0:12:55.83,main,,0000,0000,0000,,You don't get it, do you?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.11,0:12:58.16,main,,0000,0000,0000,,The theme of Meruru is friendship.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.16,0:13:02.45,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't say things just because the Maschera DVDs line up well together.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.45,0:13:03.59,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Friendship?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.97,0:13:06.95,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Where in this story is there friendship?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.95,0:13:08.85,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Please explain.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.27,0:13:14.73,main,,0000,0000,0000,,In episode six, Meruru obliterates her friend-turned-Dark Witch Al-chan using her Meteo Impact.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.73,0:13:16.98,main,,0000,0000,0000,,With a huge smile on face.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.32,0:13:19.72,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I said that was unexpected!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.72,0:13:21.73,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Nitpicking at all the small details...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.73,0:13:25.42,main,,0000,0000,0000,,And besides, she revives Al-chan during the B part!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.42,0:13:29.99,main,,0000,0000,0000,,You can bring back anyone who dies or anything that breaks in the magical field later!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.63,0:13:34.50,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Mr. Kyousuke? What's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.32,0:13:33.34,overlap,,0000,0000,0000,,What kind of a cop-out plot device is that?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.34,0:13:34.50,overlap,,0000,0000,0000,,That's ridiculous.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.76,0:13:35.76,main,,0000,0000,0000,,It's perfectly fine!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.76,0:13:38.00,main,,0000,0000,0000,,And she was saved in the end, so it worked out fine!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.76,0:13:38.00,overlap,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah whatever, fight all you want...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.00,0:13:42.84,main,,0000,0000,0000,,And anyway, what's with the constant "I'm awesome! I'm awesome!" talk in Maschera?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.76,0:13:42.84,overlap,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I guess this is friendship.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.51,0:13:50.38,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm back.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.70,0:13:55.95,main,,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.69,0:13:58.61,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Y-You...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.61,0:14:00.68,main,,0000,0000,0000,,My laptop...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.39,0:14:03.40,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Something wrong with your laptop?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.53,0:14:05.78,main,,0000,0000,0000,,You were looking at porn sites on my laptop!!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.53,0:14:09.37,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-What are you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.37,0:14:10.66,main,,0000,0000,0000,,The evidence is right there!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.00,0:14:13.23,main,,0000,0000,0000,,How could you even think of making me see something like that?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.23,0:14:14.08,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't believe it!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.08,0:14:14.91,main,,0000,0000,0000,,You're the worst!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.41,0:14:18.84,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Come on, don't cry!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.84,0:14:19.92,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not crying!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.92,0:14:21.65,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry! I'm sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.65,0:14:22.59,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I won't look at them again!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.59,0:14:24.30,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry I did it!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.70,0:14:29.68,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm calling you Porn Hunter from now on!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.68,0:14:31.68,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Please spare me that!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.33,0:14:36.93,main,,0000,0000,0000,,You're going to make up for this.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.93,0:14:38.18,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Make up?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.57,0:14:41.32,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Life counseling!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.68,0:14:47.07,main,,0000,0000,0000,,What is this?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.35,0:14:48.66,main,,0000,0000,0000,,My latest work.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.66,0:14:49.57,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Another novel.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.96,0:14:51.60,main,,0000,0000,0000,,You're still writing?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.60,0:14:53.11,main,,0000,0000,0000,,What, got a problem with that?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.11,0:14:54.58,main,,0000,0000,0000,,No, not at all!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.11,0:14:58.33,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I figured out my writing style from the last one.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.33,0:15:02.33,main,,0000,0000,0000,,So this time I figured I should just write about what I like.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.63,0:15:04.84,main,,0000,0000,0000,,And that's what this is?
Comment: 0,0:15:02.52,0:15:04.57,main,,0000,0000,0000,,<ts: My Star
Comment: 0,0:15:02.52,0:15:04.57,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Little Sister Star >
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.84,0:15:06.50,main,,0000,0000,0000,,What's it about?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.50,0:15:08.34,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Can't you tell from the title?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.63,0:15:12.97,main,,0000,0000,0000,,It's about me, an astronaut, winding up on a planet full of little sisters and doing amazing things.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.97,0:15:14.97,main,,0000,0000,0000,,That makes no sense to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.22,0:15:18.52,main,,0000,0000,0000,,It felt completely different when I finished writing it.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.52,0:15:18.98,main,,0000,0000,0000,,So...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.53,0:15:22.15,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I submitted it here.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.15,0:15:25.48,main,,0000,0000,0000,,You know the light novel publisher Raigeki Bunko?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.96,0:15:31.16,main,,0000,0000,0000,,An editor there read it and asked if I want it published as a book!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.13,0:15:34.97,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Eh? Seriously??
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.97,0:15:35.99,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.24,0:15:37.71,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Your book's getting published?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.71,0:15:38.75,main,,0000,0000,0000,,This is becoming a book??
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.75,0:15:40.34,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't shout like that!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.34,0:15:43.70,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't want Mom and Dad to know yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.70,0:15:46.38,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Also, it's not for sure yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.84,0:15:51.30,main,,0000,0000,0000,,The editor said that it's hard for readers to get into something like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.90,0:15:56.66,main,,0000,0000,0000,,But he said he could feel my passion for little sisters in the writing!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.66,0:15:59.22,main,,0000,0000,0000,,He said it was overflowing with it!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.38,0:16:04.17,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Wow. Her love for little sisters is already at a pro level...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.17,0:16:08.12,main,,0000,0000,0000,,But I don't want to touch "My Star" again.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.12,0:16:10.65,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I kind of feel like I've finished it.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.65,0:16:11.74,main,,0000,0000,0000,,She's acting like an artist already?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.81,0:16:17.37,main,,0000,0000,0000,,So I decided to write something new!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.24,0:16:28.14,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Why on earth did I have to follow my sister here to help her do research?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.94,0:16:32.92,main,,0000,0000,0000,,So, what's it about?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.17,0:16:37.05,main,,0000,0000,0000,,It takes place in a post-apocalyptic Tokyo,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.05,0:16:45.40,main,,0000,0000,0000,,and the main character goes around saving girls and rebuilding the world with them.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.40,0:16:46.56,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Exciting, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.69,0:16:50.29,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Can't you write anything normal?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.29,0:16:53.57,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm surprised that this Raigeki Bunko place would publish something like that...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.01,0:16:58.83,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I want to see what one of the characters feels for myself, if possible.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.83,0:17:02.83,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I need you to walk into the middle of that and get hit by a runaway car.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.83,0:17:04.19,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Why??
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.19,0:17:05.83,main,,0000,0000,0000,,A big one, if possible.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.83,0:17:07.05,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Like a bus or a dump truck.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.05,0:17:08.08,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll die!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.08,0:17:11.29,main,,0000,0000,0000,,It's the only way I can learn how to convey the fear and panic to my readers.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.29,0:17:15.59,main,,0000,0000,0000,,And after this incident, the main character learns how precious life is.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.59,0:17:17.67,main,,0000,0000,0000,,And my life isn't??
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.67,0:17:20.74,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Why do I have to get turned into a red splatter on the ground on Christmas?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.74,0:17:22.10,main,,0000,0000,0000,,You're useless...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.74,0:17:23.86,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Fine then.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.86,0:17:26.82,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll just figure out how to do it with some pictures.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.82,0:17:27.73,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Be grateful.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.03,0:17:30.48,main,,0000,0000,0000,,You'd better be more useful at the next spot.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.19,0:17:41.99,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, shopping here can't possibly have anything to do with your novel.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.28,0:17:44.56,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Have you even read the plot?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.56,0:17:47.54,main,,0000,0000,0000,,The main character starts by going on a date here for Christmas Eve.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.54,0:17:51.75,main,,0000,0000,0000,,After she leaves, the incident happens.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.39,0:17:55.51,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Shiori-chan survives and appears here too.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.51,0:17:57.51,main,,0000,0000,0000,,So you got this idea from an eroge?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.12,0:18:03.03,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Also, the clothes and accessories bought here are given to the little sisters in other towns.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.03,0:18:04.87,main,,0000,0000,0000,,It's an important point at the start of the book.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.87,0:18:06.52,main,,0000,0000,0000,,What kind of convenient survival is that??
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.52,0:18:09.13,main,,0000,0000,0000,,And what other towns are there, anyway?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.13,0:18:12.23,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Akiba, Otome Road, Harajuku, and Nakano Broadway.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.23,0:18:14.12,main,,0000,0000,0000,,That's completely messed up!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.12,0:18:16.78,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Anyway, buy this for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.28,0:18:19.68,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Like hell I can!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.68,0:18:22.45,main,,0000,0000,0000,,And why do you need that in the first place?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.41,0:18:26.87,main,,0000,0000,0000,,You really don't get it.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.87,0:18:30.93,main,,0000,0000,0000,,It's things like this that become emotional support in the future!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.93,0:18:33.92,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't that natural, if you receive it from the person you love?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.97,0:18:37.92,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm talking about the story in the novel, of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.68,0:18:41.26,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Come on, stop complaining and go buy it already.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.26,0:18:43.11,main,,0000,0000,0000,,There are other places we need to go.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.11,0:18:44.87,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Lend me some cash then.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.87,0:18:45.67,main,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.67,0:18:48.18,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I've only got ¥18,000 on me.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.44,0:18:52.24,main,,0000,0000,0000,,If you want to give me the difference, I'll go buy it for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.24,0:18:53.94,main,,0000,0000,0000,,You're unbelievable!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.69,0:18:57.45,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Why don't you have enough cash on you?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.45,0:19:02.20,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Who would normally be able to just slap down ¥30,000 on an accessory??
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.51,0:19:04.65,main,,0000,0000,0000,,What kind of boyfriend is this supposed to be?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.65,0:19:06.70,main,,0000,0000,0000,,A young president for a venture capitalist corporation.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.39,0:19:10.66,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Why don't you just use him for the survival story?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.66,0:19:14.23,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Instead, you're hitting him with a car and stealing his little sister?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.23,0:19:16.47,main,,0000,0000,0000,,You're pretty hardcore.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.15,0:19:18.49,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Fine then.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.49,0:19:20.65,main,,0000,0000,0000,,We can go to my usual shop.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.65,0:19:23.22,main,,0000,0000,0000,,They sell cheap but pretty accessories there.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.86,0:19:27.72,main,,0000,0000,0000,,And why do you want me to buy something for you that badly?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.24,0:19:40.18,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, next is...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.18,0:19:42.14,main,,0000,0000,0000,,There's more?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.14,0:19:44.20,main,,0000,0000,0000,,It's getting cold. Let's go home already.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.20,0:19:45.27,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Why are you complaining?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.27,0:19:47.12,main,,0000,0000,0000,,You've been useless the whole time.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.18,0:19:49.73,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.73,0:19:51.76,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm a simple high school student.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.76,0:19:54.63,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not qualified to be an author's assistant.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.45,0:19:57.38,main,,0000,0000,0000,,What, are you trying to be sarcastic?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.38,0:19:58.67,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Not really.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.67,0:20:02.73,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm just a bit annoyed at having to pay for your "research".
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.73,0:20:06.63,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Aren't you just doing this for your own self-gratification?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.78,0:20:13.89,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know what the editor told you, but your story is just ideas out of your eroge in the first place,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.89,0:20:16.06,main,,0000,0000,0000,,so it's not like you need to resear—
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.97,0:20:26.45,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Wha—
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.75,0:20:27.33,main,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you doing?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.33,0:20:32.46,main,,0000,0000,0000,,When he first finds Shiori-chan, she's standing in the pouring rain.{FOTC: When she first finds Shiori-chan, she's in the pouring rain.}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.00,0:20:40.59,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Pinned down by the debris, her screams for help are heard by no one.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.03,0:20:44.81,main,,0000,0000,0000,,She's cold, and losing hope...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.47,0:20:48.85,main,,0000,0000,0000,,The main character is the only one who hears her voice.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.31,0:20:51.66,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Well?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.66,0:20:53.72,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Pretty powerful scene, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.97,0:21:01.08,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not doing this for self-gratification or anything...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.10,0:21:03.32,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I get it.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.32,0:21:05.03,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I was wrong. Come on!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.03,0:21:06.36,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Where next?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.67,0:21:08.06,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's see...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.35,0:21:20.17,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Kyou-chan?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.17,0:21:21.64,main,,0000,0000,0000,,M-Manami?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.64,0:21:22.51,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Need something?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.38,0:21:26.92,main,,0000,0000,0000,,You said you were busy today, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.92,0:21:27.91,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.91,0:21:34.27,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I made some Christmas cake, so I was thinking if you wanted, you could come over and try some after you're done.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.03,0:21:37.65,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Alright, if I have time I'll drop by.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.65,0:21:39.25,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay! Thanks!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.25,0:21:41.27,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Why are you saying thanks?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.78,0:21:45.14,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Kyou-chan... are you...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.14,0:21:46.78,main,,0000,0000,0000,,...with a girl right now?{FOTC: Kyou-chan... are you... with a girl right now?}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.02,0:21:50.30,main,,0000,0000,0000,,W-Well, I'm with my sister...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.30,0:21:51.42,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Kirino-chan?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.42,0:21:52.25,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.25,0:21:55.63,main,,0000,0000,0000,,So you're on a Christmas date with her?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.63,0:21:58.72,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Not a date...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.14,0:22:02.48,main,,0000,0000,0000,,That shower brought me back to life.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.48,0:22:06.05,main,,0000,0000,0000,,This hotel's bathroom has some weird gadgets...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.05,0:22:06.80,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.80,0:22:07.55,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Hotel?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.55,0:22:10.30,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh no I'm losing reception!!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.30,0:22:11.23,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.23,0:22:12.90,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Were you talking to someone?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.92,0:22:15.31,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, Neighbor-girl?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.31,0:22:17.31,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Put on something, will you?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.26,0:22:19.25,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Gross!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.25,0:22:21.57,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you fantasizing about your own sister?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.57,0:22:23.32,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Siscons really are the worst.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.32,0:22:25.57,main,,0000,0000,0000,,You're the one person I don't want to hear that from!!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.00,0:22:31.57,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm supposed to spend a night here sleeping with Shiori-chan...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.57,0:22:32.97,main,,0000,0000,0000,,But that's enough research.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.97,0:22:34.58,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sensing danger from you already.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.58,0:22:36.44,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Hurry up and dry your hair and clothes already!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.44,0:22:37.60,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's leave!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.92,0:22:42.02,main,,0000,0000,0000,,So did this help at all?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.16,0:22:45.24,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Was it worth ruining your Christmas Eve?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.37,0:22:53.52,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Eureka! I've got it!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.91,0:22:57.89,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I've got a great idea!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.82,0:23:00.31,main,,0000,0000,0000,,About what?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.63,0:23:08.37,main,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.82,0:23:10.25,main,,0000,0000,0000,,The light's are going to change.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.94,0:23:24.37,main,,0000,0000,0000,,It was one messed up Christmas Eve.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.03,0:23:31.69,main,,0000,0000,0000,,But at that point I had no idea what was about to happen...
