Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.84,0:00:34.97,op-kan,,0000,0000,0000,,そんな優しくしないで　どんな顔すればいいの？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.97,0:00:38.26,op-kan,,0000,0000,0000,,積み重ねた言葉で　
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.26,0:00:43.77,op-kan,,0000,0000,0000,,見えないよ　きみの横顔
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.27,0:00:57.49,op-kan,,0000,0000,0000,,どこだっけ？　なくした鍵は見つからないままで
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.49,0:01:04.25,op-kan,,0000,0000,0000,,ため息...すれ違いに意地張って疲れちゃう
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.25,0:01:10.88,op-kan,,0000,0000,0000,,ほんの少し近く　きみとの距離が
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.88,0:01:18.05,op-kan,,0000,0000,0000,,うまく掴めないんだ　あとちょっとなのに!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.05,0:01:25.23,op-kan,,0000,0000,0000,,そんな優しくしないで　ほら　また傷つけあって
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.23,0:01:32.07,op-kan,,0000,0000,0000,,積み重ねたウソでもう　動けなくなってる
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.07,0:01:39.53,op-kan,,0000,0000,0000,,すぐに会いに行きたいけど　言葉は見つからないし
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.53,0:01:49.75,op-kan,,0000,0000,0000,,最後の一ページくらい　きみには笑顔見せたい
Comment: 0,0:01:49.75,0:01:51.71,main,,0000,0000,0000,,{Romaji}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.84,0:00:34.97,op-rom,,0000,0000,0000,,sonna yasashiku shinai de donna kao sureba ii no?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.97,0:00:38.26,op-rom,,0000,0000,0000,,tsumikasaneta kotoba de
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.26,0:00:43.77,op-rom,,0000,0000,0000,,mienai yo kimi no yokogao
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.27,0:00:57.49,op-rom,,0000,0000,0000,,dokodakke? nakushita kagi ha mitsukaranai mama de
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.49,0:01:04.25,op-rom,,0000,0000,0000,,tameiki... surechigai ni iji hatte tsukarechau
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.25,0:01:10.88,op-rom,,0000,0000,0000,,hon no sukoshi chikaku kimi to no kyori ga
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.88,0:01:18.05,op-rom,,0000,0000,0000,,umaku tsukamenainda ato chotto na no ni
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.05,0:01:25.23,op-rom,,0000,0000,0000,,sonna yasashikushinaide hora mata kizutsukeatte
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.23,0:01:32.07,op-rom,,0000,0000,0000,,tsumikasaneta uso de mou ugokenakunatteru
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.07,0:01:39.53,op-rom,,0000,0000,0000,,sugu ni ai ni ikitai kedo kotoba ha mitsukaranai shi
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.53,0:01:49.75,op-rom,,0000,0000,0000,,saigo no ichi pe-ji kurai kimi ni ha egao misetai
Comment: 0,0:00:26.96,0:00:26.96,main,,0000,0000,0000,,{Translation}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.79,0:00:34.93,op-eng,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't be so nice to me, I just don't know how to react
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.93,0:00:38.22,op-eng,,0000,0000,0000,,With all these words piling up,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.22,0:00:43.73,op-eng,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't even see your face
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.23,0:00:57.45,op-eng,,0000,0000,0000,,Where is it? I lost my key, now I can't find it
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.45,0:01:04.21,op-eng,,0000,0000,0000,,Sigh, I'll burn out if I keep acting like this whenever we fight
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.21,0:01:10.84,op-eng,,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe we're close? I just can't figure out
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.88,0:01:18.05,op-eng,,0000,0000,0000,,Just how far away I am, even though you're right there
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.05,0:01:25.23,op-eng,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't be so nice to me, see? We hurt each other again
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.23,0:01:32.07,op-eng,,0000,0000,0000,,With all these lies piling up, I can't even move
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.07,0:01:39.49,op-eng,,0000,0000,0000,,I want to see you now, but I don't know what to say
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.49,0:01:49.71,op-eng,,0000,0000,0000,,If this is the end for our story, I want you to see my smile
