Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.47,0:23:48.50,ed_kanji,,0000,0000,0000,,永遠のワルツ　貴方と
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.63,0:23:52.10,ed_kanji,,0000,0000,0000,,午前零時の鐘が鳴っても
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.56,0:23:55.20,ed_kanji,,0000,0000,0000,,私の手を離さないでね
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.67,0:23:59.21,ed_kanji,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnBalzano\fs53}Masquerade is going on {\fnDFKai-SB\fs35}さぁ踊りましょう
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.62,0:24:04.30,ed_kanji,,0000,0000,0000,,ゴシックな夜を二人で
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.76,0:23:38.09,ed_romaji,,0000,0000,0000,,Masquerade! kono yoru ha
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.37,0:23:41.51,ed_romaji,,0000,0000,0000,,doresu no kuro ni mi wo makasete
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.51,0:23:45.26,ed_romaji,,0000,0000,0000,,Now, Shall we dance? odorimashou
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.47,0:23:48.50,ed_romaji,,0000,0000,0000,,eien no warutsu anata to
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.63,0:23:52.10,ed_romaji,,0000,0000,0000,,gozen reiji no kane ga natte mo
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.56,0:23:55.20,ed_romaji,,0000,0000,0000,,watashi no te wo hanasanaide ne
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.67,0:23:59.21,ed_romaji,,0000,0000,0000,,Masquerade is going on saa odorimashou
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.62,0:24:04.30,ed_romaji,,0000,0000,0000,,goshikku na yoru wo futari de
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.76,0:23:38.09,ed_english,,0000,0000,0000,,Masquerade! For tonight
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.37,0:23:41.51,ed_english,,0000,0000,0000,,Leave yourself to the black dress
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.51,0:23:45.26,ed_english,,0000,0000,0000,,Now, shall we dance? Let me dance
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.47,0:23:48.50,ed_english,,0000,0000,0000,,An endless waltz with you
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.63,0:23:52.10,ed_english,,0000,0000,0000,,Even if midnight chimes,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.56,0:23:55.20,ed_english,,0000,0000,0000,,don’t let go my hand
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.67,0:23:59.21,ed_english,,0000,0000,0000,,Masquerade is going on, now let us dance
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.62,0:24:04.30,ed_english,,0000,0000,0000,,A gothic night together
